---
// src/components/home/AboutBrief.astro
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <p class="reveal text-xs font-medium text-accent tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">About me</p>
      <h2 class="reveal d1 font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-zinc-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-6">A bit about<br>who I am</h2>
      <p class="reveal d2 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        I'm Abdul Samad Satti, an AI/ML Engineer & Data Analyst based in Rawalpindi, Punjab. I specialize in Deep Learning, Computer Vision, and NLP. My work spans large-scale data analysis, predictive modeling, and developing intelligent systems that drive business decisions.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal d3 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        With experience as a Data Analyst Intern at Comtanix and on the OOSC educational project, I combine technical expertise with practical problem-solving. I focus on building solutions that matter—from analyzing operational datasets to developing advanced AI frameworks.
      </p>
      
      <a href="/about" class="reveal d4 inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-accent text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-display font-bold text-sm hover:bg-accent-light transition-all shimmer mb-12">
        Read more about me →
      </a>

      <div class="reveal d4 w-full">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">AI & ML Stack</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2" role="list" aria-label="Skills">
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Python</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Deep Learning</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Computer Vision</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">NLP</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Laravel & PHP</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Docker / Podman</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Git & GitHub</span>
          <span role="listitem" class="stag text-sm bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:border-accent">Astro / Tailwind</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
